    body: "## What's Changed\n* model replacements: prevent duplicate processing by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3789\n* jak3: fix cloth disappearing after 600 orbs by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3790\n* jak1: add merc version of `draw-bones-hud` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3793\n* [sound] Add instance limits by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3769\n* Add option to hide the imgui bar with a click event by @Zedb0T in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3791\n* Fix animation processing interpolation bug, crash on no merc material by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3794\n* decompiler: detect and turn inverse mult to div by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3795\n* [Custom Levels] Improve color palette generation by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3797\n* custom models: option to copy mod/eye draws from original model by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3800\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3779\n* custom actor, fix animation compression by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3802\n* [Jak3] Adjust overlord SPU dma to avoid audio hangs by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3804\n* jak3: fix missing shadow for wings by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3803\n* [jak3] Fix issue where some vag streams never queue by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3805\n* fonts: support caron diacritics by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3815\n* fonts: add support for the rest of the czech alphabet by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3816\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3809\n* [jak3] Avoid language 255 issue by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3818\n* [jak3] Update texture remap table by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3821\n* [jak2, jak3] Unstretch moon and sun by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3822\n* [graphics] Improve some camera math by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3825\n* [gk] Increase print buffer, add size check by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3826\n* [jak3] Fix cloth nans by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3827\n* jak3 pc subtitles by @Aloqas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3812\n* jak3: port `anim-tester-x` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3830\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.2.20...v0.2.21",
