    body: "## What's Changed\r\n* [jak3] Fix for precd extraction by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3744\r\n* docs: Remove instructions to add go-task tap to Homebrew. by @mrpippy in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3751\r\n* Fix sprite3_3d.vert on macOS by @mrpippy in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3750\r\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3749\r\n* Support Apple Silicon via Rosetta2 on MacOS Sequoia and Above by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3754\r\n* deps: commit rapidjson with 8 year old fix by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3755\r\n* jak3: `subtitle3`, `vag-player` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3758\r\n* Fix crash in ocean-far with invalid DMA size by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3746\r\n* [jak2] Fix bug where spinning into grind doesnt break clasps in dig1 by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3740\r\n* macOS: Fix issue causing only part of the window to be rendered to by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3756\r\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3757\r\n* [jak3] Fix overlord soundbank unload, fix warnings by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3762\r\n* [jak3] Fix stack layout for car spawn by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3765\r\n* jak3: speedrunner mode by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3761\r\n* [jak3] workaround for intro crash on screen filter by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3770\r\n* Create separate x86_64 and ARM64 macOS targets. by @mrpippy in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3760\r\n* jak3: fix ragdolls settling too early by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3775\r\n* custom models: envmap support by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3777\r\n* Taskfile: Call 'python3' on non-Windows platforms by @mrpippy in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3752\r\n* ci: update minimum macOS supported version to Ventura (13) by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3780\r\n* jak1, jak2: add `get-texture` macro by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3778\r\n* custom models: increase default joint count by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3782\r\n* jak3: fix music not pausing by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3783\r\n* custom models: better error for invalid envmap material by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3784\r\n* Remove 128 character buffer causing long filenames to crash gk by @massimilianodelliubaldini in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3771\r\n* custom models: ignore invalid envmap material by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3785\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @mrpippy made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3751\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.2.18...v0.2.20",
