    body: "## What's Changed\n* build(deps): bump peter-evans/create-pull-request from 6 to 7 by @dependabot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3694\n* [jak1] Patch \"NG+ glitch\" by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3690\n* github: switch to using issue types were applicable in issue forms by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3696\n* extractor: add error code messages around `3990` by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3699\n* [jak3] Fix flashing with maker projectiles by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3702\n* [jak3] fix envmap texture and strength by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3704\n* [jak3] Add merc fade and support for no texture flag by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3710\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3711\n* decompiler: fix `secret-disable` form in `defskelgroup` detection by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3713\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3714\n* Parameterize the iso_data folder for goalc by @massimilianodelliubaldini in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3692\n* game: fix game icon aspect ratio by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3718\n* [jak3] Fix target marker texture by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3721\n* [jak3] Fix neosat particles and tentacle by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3722\n* g/j2: make the turret controls respect the camera settings by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3715\n* game: Update game's GPU test to output the GPU vendor info by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3717\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3726\n* [jak3] Misc texture anim fixes by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3732\n* [jak3] Support texture anim in TIE by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3734\n* [jak2,3] Support loading clut blender animated textures to the pool by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3735\n* [custom levels] A few bug fixes by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3736\n* custom levels: add `draco` lib to support compressed glb files by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3723\n* Update LICENSE, and add jak 2/3 iso_data folders by @Zedb0T in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3738\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3737\n* [jak2] Correct behavior of hint subtitles toggle by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3741\n* game: move `pc-encode-utf8-string` to common `kmachine` code by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3742\n* jak2: fix consite crash by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3743\n\n## New Contributors\n* @massimilianodelliubaldini made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3692\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.2.17...v0.2.18",
