    body: "## What's Changed\n* build(deps): bump hendrikmuhs/ccache-action from 1.2.13 to 1.2.14 by @dependabot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3650\n* Create `abutton-idx` enum, replace magic numbers across codebase by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3646\n* jak3: fix vagdir bit-field for msvc + clang on windows by @VodBox in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3643\n* Use custom normals in model replacement! by @The-Stellar in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3649\n* decompiler: `call-parent-state-handler` and `suspend-for` macros by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3625\n* jak3: decomp `bigmap`, `blit-displays`, fix `progress` crash by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3657\n* [jak2] Workaround for sound effects getting dropped by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3660\n* Fix github release-pipeline so version tag is available for cmake by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3651\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3661\n* cmake: handle the scenario of a commit having more than 1 tag by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3662\n* Background improvements for custom levels by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3672\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3666\n* [jak2] english subtitle fixes by @Aloqas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3665\n* ubuntu Dockerfile fix a missing dependency by @ImaDoor2785 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3667\n* [jak3] Fix bomb bot bombs disappearing by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3674\n* [jak3] Fix crash with volcano platforms by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3676\n* jak3: misc fixes by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3686\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3687\n* custom levels: support vanilla skies and texture remapping tables by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3691\n* game: dont filter resolutions in windowed mode by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3688\n* g/j2: Fix subtitle setting persisting and add a toggle for the hint subtitles by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3689\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3693\n\n## New Contributors\n* @The-Stellar made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3649\n* @ImaDoor2785 made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3667\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.2.16...v0.2.17",
