    body: "## What's Changed\n* build(deps): bump hendrikmuhs/ccache-action from 1.2.12 to 1.2.13 by @dependabot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3497\n* jak3: fix mirage shot by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3501\n* ci: pin to avx for macos by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3502\n* fix another jak 1 level name by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3503\n* fix c++ compiler warnings, extract_merc assert by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3488\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3507\n* decomp3: traffic/citizen/faction code, `desert-rescue` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3506\n* Add hfrag, clean up some background renderer stuff by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3509\n* jak3: fix local space particle info crash by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3511\n* Intro palace DGOs by @BreakPoints in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3512\n* decomp3: more misc files by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3513\n* Jak3 sky by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3514\n* Dependency graph work - Part 1 - Preliminary work by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3505\n* jak3: fix hud sprite crash + add entity debugger by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3516\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3517\n* goalc: add a performance report feature by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3519\n* decomp3: decompile remaining mission code by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3515\n* jak3: custom level support by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3522\n* Start setting up texture animation for jak 3. by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3524\n* [wip] build actor tool by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3266\n* jak3: sprite limit increase + add bsphere toggle for region faces by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3529\n* jak 3 shadows by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3530\n* jak3: shadow culling hack + finish region debugging tools + fix bigmap crashes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3532\n* Add periods to lines in code_status.md for consistency by @richarm4 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3521\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3528\n* game: fix the path the`--portable` flag determines by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3537\n* g/j2: add some debug menu options to unlock things and give orbs/gems/ammo by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3539\n* [buildactor] support generating `collide-mesh`es for custom models by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3540\n* jak3 - fill out some `text-id` entries by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3494\n* [jak2] new subtitle speakers by @Aloqas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3536\n* [jak3] implement autocollect and city turbo board cheats, fix actor heap and level flags by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3541\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.2.12...v0.2.13",
