    body: "\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* decomp3: add background data to pc renderers, get mood and time of day stuff running by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3450\r\n* Jak 3, fixes for animation issues, rm debug print by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3453\r\n* [goalc] speed up jak3 compilation by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3454\r\n* decomp3: eye renderer and more files by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3457\r\n* [jak3] Support jaextern.str, stub for blue fog fix by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3455\r\n* fix typo by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3458\r\n* [jak3] Fix defskelgroup by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3460\r\n* decomp3: lightning renderer, nav code, texture remap, fix progress menu crash by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3461\r\n* [jak3] Minimap texture fix by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3465\r\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3462\r\n* Fix bad speedrun Select pause behavior by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3464\r\n* [jak3] remove some stubs and fix health bar by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3468\r\n* [jak3] implement pckernel by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3472\r\n* [jak3] fix process stack overflow + collision renderer by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3473\r\n* debugger: reverse the order the backtrace is printed by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3474\r\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3471\r\n* decomp3: more misc files by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3466\r\n* jak3: fix type by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3478\r\n* jak3 pc: math-camera, letterbox, led and auto-save by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3479\r\n* fix minimap icon misalign by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3481\r\n* jak2/3: re-implement screenshot system through goal by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3482\r\n* jak3: fix some collide decomp + fix projectiles aiming at intangible objects by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3485\r\n* Fix \"logical not is only applied to the left hand side of comparison\" warnings by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3484\r\n* jak3: hack level heap sizes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3487\r\n* decomp3: font widescreen and shadow hacks, generic renderer, misc files by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3483\r\n* extractor: support extracting using a folder path by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3422\r\n* game: allow overriding the config directory location by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3477\r\n* more debug information when RPC buffers exhaust by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3490\r\n* decomp3 `title-obs`, `credits-h` by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3476\r\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3491\r\n* use only the real level name in the Loader by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3495\r\n* custom levels: don't uppercase FR3 filename by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3496\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.2.10...v0.2.11",
