    body: "## What's Changed\n* deps: update `fmt` to latest version by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3403\n* deps: SDL update to 2.30.0 by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3384\n* ci: move to `sccache` by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3404\n* ci: move to macos-12 by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3407\n* Fix issues with camera movement with controller when mouse tracking is also enabled by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3409\n* [jak3] Decompile sprite by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3412\n* Fix minor issues related to the speedrunner mode menu, also stop saving the `pc-settings` every frame when sr mode is on by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3413\n* d/j3: ensure type-tests pass by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3414\n* g/j2: Update some `vehicle` related naming by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3419\n* g/j2: workaround intermittent lifeseed DMA crash by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3418\n* [jak3] Decompile sprite and debug files by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3420\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3423\n* decomp3: more engine stuff, support boxed stack arrays in compiler by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3424\n* Port `bones.gc` math to GOAL by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3425\n* [goal] Add labels, break, and continue to loops by @Brent-Hickey in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3426\n* Decompile foreground and bones by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3427\n* Decompile font, decomp, background, shrubbery by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3428\n* Decompile tfrag, tie, prim by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3429\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3430\n* decomp3: more engine files, `get-texture` macro, use `print` method in autogenerated inspect, fix bitfield float print by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3432\n* Decompile `level` by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3433\n* decomp drawable, main by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3434\n* [jak3] A bunch of small fixes to get `game.cgo` to load by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3435\n* decomp3: more engine stuff, fix `ja` macro detection for jak 2/3, unmerged `let` matcher, `part-tracker-spawn` macro by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3436\n* LSP: A bunch of new OpenGOAL language features by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3437\n* g/j1: remove the redundant graphics menu by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3421\n* decomp3: support for virtual states inheriting from their own type's virtual states, `gun-yellow-shot`, `gun-red-shot`, `gun-dark-shot` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3438\n* goalc: Fix new symbol trie's performance inefficiencies by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3443\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3444\n* decompiler: allow overriding dgo inputs by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3446\n* build(deps): bump mathieudutour/github-tag-action from 6.1 to 6.2 by @dependabot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3442\n* goalc: add some nullptr checks around symbol map lookups by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3447\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.2.8...v0.2.9",
