    body: "## What's Changed\n* decomp3: more misc files by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3349\n* [jak3] More headers! by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3351\n* build(deps): bump peter-evans/repository-dispatch from 2 to 3 by @dependabot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3354\n* build(deps): bump peter-evans/create-pull-request from 5 to 6 by @dependabot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3353\n* Change important `printf`s to `lg::print` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3355\n* decomp3: more headers by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3356\n* [jak3] More headers again by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3352\n* seriously fix music player in title screen by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3358\n* game: fix intermittent sprite_distort related crash by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3357\n* decomp3: more headers (again) by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3362\n* [jak3] More headers again again by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3359\n* [jak3] More headers, up to load-dgo by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3363\n* [jak3] decomp gsound by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3364\n* d/j3: do a few `mood` related files and fix some issues along the way by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3365\n* decomp: Copy over new docstrings back to jak 2's common code, write some scripts to help automate this by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3366\n* decompiler: `defskelgroup` macro detection for jak 3, fix art group dumping for jak 3 and some more decomp work by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3370\n* Decompile `joint`, `collide-func`, clean up joint decompression code for all games by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3369\n* [jak3] `joint-mod`, `subdivide`, `bsp` by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3371\n* decomp `loader` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3373\n* decomp3: `game-info`, `game-task`, `game-save`, `level-info`, `process-drawable` and more by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3374\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3368\n* Update to C++20 by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3193\n* Fix remaining cpp20 issues by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3375\n* Switch to std::span by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3376\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3379\n* lsp: revert unnamed variable labelling by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3381\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3382\n* tracing: add some more startup related events and a new `--profile-until-event` flag by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3385\n* g/j2: properly wireup mouse settings, properly detect when the mouse has stopped moving by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3383\n* g/j2: allow customizing the speedrunner menu bind by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3386\n* Rename `bigmap-id` enum entries by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3380\n* game: disable keyboard input by default, give users a way to enable it via the imgui menu by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3295\n* [high fps] Increase input buffer size and fix cloud scroll speed by @Brent-Hickey in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3178\n* g/j2: Dynamic speedrun mode categories and implement a significant amount of a practice mode by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3378\n* Only remove -vis from name if it is part of the name. by @LuminarLight in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3257\n* scripts: new linter script to detect goal_src files with trailing whitespace by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3387\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3389\n* formatter: Format `deftype` correctly by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3391\n* Fix `(-> *autosplit-info-jak1* training-num-orbs)` when blacked out by @Zedb0T in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3297\n* decomp3: more engine stuff, detect non-virtual state inheritance by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3377\n* [joint] fix missing matrix interpolation by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3394\n* decomp: update naming across jak2/3 by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3395\n* jak2 pckernel: save `pc-settings` on cheat progress and regular auto-saves by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3396\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3397\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.2.7...v0.2.8",
