    zipball_url:
      "https://api.github.com/repos/open-goal/jak-project/zipball/v0.2.7",
    body: "## What's Changed\n* formatter: support for a few more forms and fix some bugs, update tree-sitter grammar by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3317\n* lsp: handle line-endings appropriately by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3318\n* j2-overlord: Fix typo by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3320\n* decomp3: some engine files by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3319\n* [jak3] Decompile `gcommon` by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3321\n* [jak2] fix music player option by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3323\n* custom levels: `cell-info` and `buzzer-info` lumps by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3324\n* lsp: flag unnamed variables in IR files by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3325\n* [gltf] Support either u16 or float for colors by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3322\n* [jak3] Decomp for gkernel, gkernel-h, gstate, gstring by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3326\n* decomp3: `geometry`, `vector`, `timer-h`, ocean table files and `game-task` related enums by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3329\n* decompiler: Extract Jak3 VAGs by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3328\n* [jak3] A few early files by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3330\n* decomp3: `timer`, `display-h`, `decomp-h`, `file-io`, `pad` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3332\n* decomp3: `loader-h`, `capture-h`, `math-camera-h`, `math-camera`, `connect`, `gs`, `texture-h` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3333\n* formatter: fix multi-line form consolidation by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3336\n* custom levels: add support for `symbol`, `type`, and `string` lumps by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3337\n* decomp: add a new config flag to disable var-name casts by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3338\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3327\n* fix custom screenshots and change screenshot directory by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3339\n* jak3: dump of all vu programs by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3340\n* decomp3: `font-h`, `display`, `profile`, `settings-h`, `camera-defs-h`, `text-h` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3335\n* [jak3] dma, dma-bucket, dma-buffer by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3331\n* [jak3] dma-disasm, time-of-day-h, texture-anim-h, level-h by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3344\n* cmake: Remove -Wmissing-include-dir by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3343\n* [jak3] misc. headers by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3345\n* [jak3] decompile (but not port) texture by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3346\n* [jak3] Drawable header decomp by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3347\n* Rip collision based on config flag by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3348\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.2.6...v0.2.7",
