    body: "## What's Changed\n* 989snd: sound bank loading overhaul by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3185\n* [jak2] Fix unicode issue with GAME.CGO load by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3254\n* fix weird potential initialization bug with the music log by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3258\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3255\n* add ms to loader output by @trippjoe in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3261\n* Disable save_texture_pngs by default [jak1] by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3256\n* French subtitle_lines_fr-FR.json by @RoyalForgotten in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3259\n* g/j2: save window-size to pc-settings when it's changed by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3263\n* g/j2: fix interleaving of local and external highscores by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3264\n* g/j2: switch to OpenGOAL speedrun.com leaderboards by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3265\n* [jak2] fix shadow origin using wrong joint by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3271\n* [jak2] implement pc cheats in menu by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3275\n* Impr: Make mesh extract compatible with gLTF 2.0 (and Blender 4.0) by @EvelynTSMG in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3268\n* j2-overlord: Clean up some VAG functions by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3287\n* build(deps): bump actions/upload-artifact from 3 to 4 by @dependabot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3284\n* build(deps): bump actions/download-artifact from 3 to 4 by @dependabot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3283\n* Support extracting collision to obj for jak2/3 formats by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3292\n* d/j3: all-types: guess at associated process for non-virtual states and fix some issues along the way by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3300\n* game: Fix issues related to remapping with SDL axii's (ie. triggers) by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3294\n* [jak2] implement statistics tracker by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3288\n* Fix cases of string formatting with non string literals by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3304\n* custom levels: enum lump support by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3305\n* [pckernel] use `pc-get-resolution` to fetch initial fullscreen resolution by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3307\n* deps: update zydis to latest commit by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3306\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.2.4...v0.2.5",
