      "https://api.github.com/repos/open-goal/jak-project/zipball/v0.2.3",
    body: '## What\'s Changed\n* fix mistakes in `projectiles.gc` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3187\n* formatter: Add support for a few common functions and fix an LSP startup issue by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3190\n* reduce glow renderer vram usage + raise glow sprite limit by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3194\n* fix forest youngsamos crash when he runs out of health by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3197\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3200\n* Update subtitle_lines_fr-FR.json by @RoyalForgotten in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3201\n* j2: fix enemy-method-135 by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3206\n* i18n: transcribe missing english subtitles by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3199\n* Update subtitle_lines_it-IT.json by @Radu13 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3208\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3211\n* [jak2] extended shadows hack + add/fix progress options by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3213\n* fix dark jak punch sound and some samos sounds by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3214\n* i18n: fix filepath for jak 2 subtitle translation file by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3217\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3218\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3215\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3226\n* [Loader] Unload less stuff per frame by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3227\n* [jak2] adjust progress generic item sizes + add scrolling effect by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3231\n* [jak2] split language and text language by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3233\n* [jak2] Support per-proto shrub visibility by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3228\n* Allow replacing all instances of a texture with one texture by @LuminarLight in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3234\n* jak2: add vehicle hijack lines PC cheat by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3205\n* [jak2] Fix "Select controller" by @SuperSamus in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3191\n\n## New Contributors\n* @RoyalForgotten made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3201\n* @Radu13 made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3208\n* @SuperSamus made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3191\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.2.2...v0.2.3',
