    body: "\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* docs: Re-order root README a bit and add new link to new tutorial by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3119\r\n* ci: properly statically link on macOS by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3127\r\n* g/jak2: allow `L1 + R1 + Start` to open speedrun menu as well by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3131\r\n* g/jak2: disable speech volume when starting a new speedrun by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3132\r\n* Add fallback text functionality to Jak 2 by @Zedb0T in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3128\r\n* Translated Jak 2 Game Texts to Spanish by @xsm2 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3139\r\n* Jak 2 French Game Text by @Blqnc in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3138\r\n* [jak2]do not force UK english on PAL by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3142\r\n* [jak2] Hopefully improve sky performance by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3130\r\n* i18n: Add jak 2 custom text to Crowdin by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3141\r\n* [jak2] Try to fix glow again by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3144\r\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3146\r\n* allow per-file override of type-to-artgroup map + use correct divide by zero handler in `civilian.gc` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3148\r\n* [jak2] Fix palace rotation at high fps by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3147\r\n* [jak2] Pass 0x01 through format by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3143\r\n* g/j2: Add ending condition checks to the autosplitter struct by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3155\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @Blqnc made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3138\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.44...v0.2.0",
