    zipball_url:
      "https://api.github.com/repos/open-goal/jak-project/zipball/v0.1.44",
    body: "\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3060\r\n* decompiler: better automatic detection of art groups and `joint-node-index` macro detection by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3061\r\n* [jak2] Set up extractor by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3042\r\n* [goalc] Cleaned up speedups by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3066\r\n* [jak2] new glow fix by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3067\r\n* decompiler: some hacks to allow running decompiler on jak 3 v5 code files, improve `all-types` generation by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2526\r\n* [glow] potentially fix bad glow texture by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3071\r\n* [jak2] fix minor original game visual bugs by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3072\r\n* github: add issue template for jak 2 by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3073\r\n* jak3: add `goal_src` skeleton by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3069\r\n* [decompiler] Support v5 data file link data by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3076\r\n* decompiler: fix for v5 art group info dump, update `taskfile` for jak 3 by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3077\r\n* decompiler: allow jak 3 texture and model extraction by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3080\r\n* [jak2] Fix collision renderer extract by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3081\r\n* g/j2: Integrate highscores with Speedrun.com/JakSpeedruns.com when speedrunner mode is enabled by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3037\r\n* [jak1] Finnish base game strings by @Aloqas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3058\r\n* jak3: add missing files and implement `pexcw` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3084\r\n* decompiler: add texture merging feature by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3083\r\n* fix `*jak1-full-game*` being flipped by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3085\r\n* [glb export] Export bones. by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3087\r\n* custom levels: support for packing textures by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3089\r\n* Fix build failure at llvm-rc on windows due to codepage error on zydis by @jabermony in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3088\r\n* jak2: add warning text when changing frame rate for the first time by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3092\r\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3091\r\n* Add label_types file merge for PAL version by @jabermony in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3086\r\n* ci: Workaround CMake/Perl regression in recent windows-2022 images by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3097\r\n* formatter: rewrite and refactor, address more edge-cases, begin documenting my work by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3096\r\n* custom levels: refactor level building code and jak 2 support by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3090\r\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3101\r\n* Fix starting continue point for Hub 2/3 category extensions by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3103\r\n* [compiler] asm-only disasm output + fix spacing bug by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3104\r\n* `deftype` and `defmethod` syntax major changes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3094\r\n* [jak2] simplify fps disclaimer by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3108\r\n* fps selection fixes i missed by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3109\r\n* rename joint node and art element macros by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3111\r\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3113\r\n* ci/windows: stop Strawberry perl from changing resulting built artifacts in CI by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3114\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @Aloqas made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3058\r\n* @jabermony made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3088\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.43...v0.1.44",
