    body: "## What's Changed\n* [gltf export] Export TIE wind models by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2960\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2926\n* entity-debug: Show path and volume data. by @LuminarLight in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2942\n* Update subtitle_en-US.json by @atylmo in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2763\n* g/j2: Some more work on the SQL editor - dump and seed `light` data by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2954\n* decomp: handle dumping jak 2 VAG file assets by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2969\n* jak2: add frame rate option to graphics menu by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2962\n* [jak2] Fix hover-formation decomp by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2971\n* [jak1] Fix duplicated tie extract by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2972\n* g/j2: Start adding game options to jak 2's menu by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2968\n* Save entities to JSON, and make custom level building a little faster by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2973\n* jak2: macro detection for `launch-particles` and `seconds-per-frame`, add `og:preserve-this` comments for manual patches by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2974\n* g/j2: revert signature changes to `cam-setting-data`, fix camera regressions by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2975\n* [jak 2] Export the collision mesh by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2977\n* g/j1: resolve memory leak around display/input dynamic strings from C++ by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2979\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2980\n* Polish translation for Jak 1 by @rafalekkB in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2961\n* CI: check for removed goal_src code that we want or need to perserve by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2987\n* [jak2] placeholder subtitle files by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2986\n* [decompiler] decomp jak2 `static-attack-info` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2992\n* [jak2] fix `task-arrow-spawn` decomp by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2995\n* gsrc: add more `og:preserve-this` comments by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2996\n* g/j2: Implement speedrunner mode in jak 2 by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2976\n* Update game_base_text_pl-PL.json by @rafalekkB in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2997\n* jak2: fix `metalkor` regression by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2999\n* goalc: add `macro-expand` form by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3000\n* ci: separate lint checks into a required and optional workflow by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3002\n* [jak2] ckernel: implement `loado` and `load_and_link` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3005\n* decomp: fix some `enemy` decomp by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3008\n* [opengoal] make `none` a child of `object` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3001\n* [jak2] fully implement collide mesh renderer by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3010\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3006\n* improve decomp of state handlers and art groups by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3014\n* g/j2: speed up level-select menu scrolling by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3013\n* [jak2] also allow analog for play select fast scroll by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3015\n* g/j2: Fill out `game options` menu by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3003\n* scripts: remove unused `code_retention` script code by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3019\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3025\n* fix `(font-flags left)` name + fix `right` flag not reflecting in debug text box by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3020\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3028\n* [compiler] fix `compile_condition` not attempting macro expansion by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3030\n* decompiler: `obj` -> `this`, `set-time!` and `time-elapsed?` macros by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3026\n* [decompiler] do not use `time-elapsed?` on unsigned comps by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3031\n* misc low hanging fruit fixes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3034\n* Jak 2 controller LED implementation by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3035\n* [jak2] un-mips2c `draw-string` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3040\n* Remove dupe line in discord-rpc .clang-format by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3039\n* [decompiler] Handle `find-parent-method` by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3018\n* [jak2] scalable debug font + fix debug menu widescreen bugs by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3044\n* fix draw-string-xy-scaled cropping by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3041\n* [jak2] fully implement `*user*` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3046\n* Bump actions/checkout from 3 to 4 by @dependabot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3047\n* g/j2: don't force auto-save on in jak 2 when starting a speedrun by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/3048\n\n## New Contributors\n* @atylmo made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2763\n* @rafalekkB made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2961\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.41...v0.1.42",
