    body: "\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* fix collision renderer filters not working by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2872\r\n* [goalc] Sign extend objects when loading them by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2863\r\n* Anim Tester X - Quality of Life improvements by @LuminarLight in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2682\r\n* Basic hash table and jump table by @Brent-Hickey in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1837\r\n* github: update issue templates, move general feature requests to discussions preferably by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2879\r\n* jak1: start a new game correctly when speedrunner mode is enabled by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2873\r\n* formatter: support formatting bindings, for example in a `let` by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2883\r\n* [jak2] get new cheats working by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2885\r\n* [jak2] progress: make custom aspect ratio menu by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2888\r\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2889\r\n* [jak2] prepare `scf-get-territory` usage by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2890\r\n* log: rotate log files with timestamps and add flag to disable ANSI colors by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2886\r\n* custom levels: fix crash when more than one ambient is present by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2891\r\n* log: don't recursively iterate when rotating log files by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2892\r\n* cleanup our cmake and build warnings by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2876\r\n* cmake: fix regression for building SDL statically by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2894\r\n* input: fix double press issue when assigning a bind by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2895\r\n* Update test-zone.jsonc to use lowercase for nickname by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2896\r\n* [jak1] Fix texture-related custom level crash by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2898\r\n* [shrub] Fix bug with gs-prim settings by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2899\r\n* [glow] fix clipping bug by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2902\r\n* log: ensure the `log/` directory exists by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2904\r\n* 989snd: implement SetVolPan for midi sounds by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2905\r\n* [jak 2] bigmap, fix texture filtering on map icons by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2906\r\n* [jak2] fix bad blerc on objects with warp by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2907\r\n* [jak2] music player cheat menu by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2900\r\n* [jak2] small minor fixes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2909\r\n* [jak2] fix bug in direct in texture handler by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2910\r\n* handle texture of 0 in extract_tie by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2911\r\n* [jak2] fix glow sprite flickering by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2912\r\n* Fix alpha test > vs >= (minimap arrow fix) by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2913\r\n* [jak2] Support Japanese Subtitles by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2914\r\n* [jak2] Support `draw-raw-image` by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2915\r\n* [jak2] widescreen fix for splash/jp subtitles by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2916\r\n* [jak2] fix a few silly texture bugs by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2917\r\n* jak1: Consolidate art-elts into a single file as is done in jak 2 by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2887\r\n* [jak 2] Clouds V2, Clean up texture animator by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2921\r\n* [jak2] Toxic Slime texture animations by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2922\r\n* [jak2] Fix depth testing issues on glow sprites by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2923\r\n* [jak2] a few more subtitles + L1/R1 to move *much* faster through debug menu by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2925\r\n* [jak2] fill in a lot of flags for decomp + mouse macros by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2927\r\n* [jak2] minimap improvements by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2929\r\n* g/j1: add support for missing polish alphabet characters by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2931\r\n* ckernel: fix file paths for art groups and tpages by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2932\r\n* custom levels: add support for packing models and textures into the FR3 file by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2936\r\n* [jak2] fix bugs with incorrect music playing sometimes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2938\r\n* various subtitle editor fixes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2941\r\n* ci: macOS build with big sur to increase compatibility by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2944\r\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2945\r\n* Placeholder strings for future Jak 2 features + minor subtitle editor fixes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2943\r\n* [extractor] fix territory being set to wrong value by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2946\r\n* [sprite3] fix max sprite number being wrong by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2949\r\n* [jak2] fix bug in `outro-port` script by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2952\r\n* [jak2] higher resolution cloud textures by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2951\r\n* [sprite] Adjust allocation randomization by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2953\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.39...v0.1.40",
