    body: '## What\'s Changed\n* Make all project targets compile on Intel MacOS by @fabjan in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2780\n* change imgui toggle key from leftalt to f12 by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2794\n* [decompiler] new features + fixes, + other jak2 fixes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2796\n* Make setup_cpu_info work on (Intel) Macs by @fabjan in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2798\n* [jak2] add some missing lambdas by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2799\n* [jak1] Merc for title - fixes blerc by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2801\n* repl: separate history by game version by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2805\n* rework jak 2 goal file structure by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2806\n* fix some rare enum detection bugs by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2808\n* [decompiler] fix in-place ops not getting detected sometimes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2810\n* jak2: fix race crash by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2816\n* input: Hopefully make keyboard/mouse handling more consistent by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2807\n* Make Jak1 playable on macOS (intel) by @fabjan in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2811\n* fix mouse mispositioning when letterboxed by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2818\n* add (Intel) macOS job and artifacts to release pipeline by @fabjan in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2817\n* i18n: subtitle code cleanup and update new subtitle JSON files to be compatible with Crowdin by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2802\n* fix subtitle console spam + font shadow offseting by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2822\n* increase max minimap icons 64 -> 256 by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2826\n* improve `send-event` for jak 2 by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2828\n* [jak2] Work-in-progress texture animations by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2819\n* [jak2] speed up the sky texture animation by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2829\n* Added bound check for blend vertex count by @animalstyletaco in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2830\n* Get the project compiling on Apple Silicon macOS natively (arm64) by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2827\n* [jak2] More texture animations by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2831\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2832\n* [jak2] Fix overlord related crash by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2834\n* [jak2] More progress on texture animations by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2835\n* [jak2] Add static textures for the progress menu by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2838\n* game: add a clear text label for how to hide the top bar by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2845\n* [jak2] Fix dark jak anim and low res skull gems by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2842\n* [jak2] make progress menu work for widescreen + various other fixes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2843\n* Fix small buzz motor not vibrating correctly by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2846\n* fix stad-samos regression from refactor (#2796) + change imgui toggle to left-alt and make it customizable by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2848\n* [jak2] More texture animations, and fixes by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2847\n* Fix possible crash when loading files by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2850\n* [jak1] Fix ice walking animation bug and crash by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2851\n* [jak2] graphic options menu proof of concept by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2849\n* `force-actors?` -> `ps2-actor-vis?` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2852\n* [jak2] workaround for missing yakow textures by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2854\n* [jak2] fix transparent shrub blending by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2853\n* [jak2] Fix ocean culling when using camera-other by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2858\n* [jak2] fix compile error by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2862\n* [jak2] use current buffer for blit-displays by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2855\n* [jak2] disable envmap when it should be by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2864\n* [gfx] Clean up background renderer matrices, fix "hole covers" by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2866\n* ci: strip binaries in their respective runners by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2868\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2869\n* fix texture anim shader on macOS by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2870\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.38...v0.1.39',
