    body: "## What's Changed\n* i18n: init translation files that can be used by crowdin by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1760\n* Initial Jak 2 Autosplit Support by @Zedb0T in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2239\n* alternate method for scaling screen warp effects with aspect ratio by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2603\n* [goalc] default to non-immediate lambdas if not requested by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2604\n* game: don't exit prematurely when rebooting in debug by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2608\n* Bump peter-evans/create-pull-request from 4 to 5 by @dependabot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2609\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2610\n* decomp: `ctywide-speech` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2612\n* i18n: allow for multiple file sources per language by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2613\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2614\n* start `blit-displays` decomp & renderer + improve decompilation of some DMA macros by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2616\n* fix blit size being wrong most of the time by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2620\n* pack tfrag normals into 10 bits by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2625\n* [jak2] combined shadow work PR by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2632\n* cmake: sort `game/CMakeLists.txt` files by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2633\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2639\n* jak1: fix regression with npc NaNs by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2642\n* i18n: Lookup untranslated strings from a fallback language (english) instead of displaying `Unknown...` by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2637\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2645\n* fix shadow colors in jak 1 and jak 2 shadow crash by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2647\n* fix racer hud regression by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2648\n* jak1: add back money starburst by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2650\n* small jak 2 bug fixes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2649\n* small cleanup to `progress-draw.gc` and `set-font-color` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2653\n* Support multiline text (e.g. credits) override with JSON format by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2629\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2651\n* better decomp of `set-subtask-hook!`, `sub-task-list` array and `*-setting!` macros by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2654\n* jak2: fill out names for `text-id` enum by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2640\n* fix `stadium-obs` regression by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2661\n* Fix GCC13 build by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2641\n* jak2: add `current-time` macro for process clocks by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2662\n* vag player + skill tracker debug tools and fix some decomp by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2664\n* Hungarian Custom Text JSON Disappearance fix, and translating new speedrun text by @LuminarLight in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2665\n* i18n: Create a JSON subtitle format for translating via Crowdin by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2644\n* New Crowdin updates by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2666\n* i18n: add MysticGamer23's swedish subtitles by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2667\n* [jak 2] Fix possible stereo desync in overlord by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2663\n* LSP: OpenGOAL Feature Support - Part 1 by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2668\n* Update `font-color` enum by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2670\n* overlord: Some cleanup by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2669\n* fix: add unicode tree-sitter include directory by @f46b83ee9 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2674\n* formatter: initial and basic indentation/alignment and expose the formatting via the LSP by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2673\n* jak2: fix `pegasus` crash by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2676\n* jak2: fix race crash by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2680\n\n## New Contributors\n* @f46b83ee9 made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2674\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.35...v0.1.36",
