    body: '## What\'s Changed\n* lsp: fix route handling json error by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2448\n* fix repl buffer overrun + use a different port for each game version by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2449\n* jak2: add some temporary `gui-control` hacks to make missions completable by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2454\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2452\n* Translate new Jak 1 speedrunning text to Hungarian, plus some minor adjustments by @LuminarLight in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2242\n* add a temporary gui-control hack to make boulder chase mission completable by @Zedb0T in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2455\n* jak1: clean up all `dummy` methods by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2457\n* fix alpha blend bit for jak 1 merc by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2458\n* make directrenderer in sprite work + rename `game-text-id` to `text-id` + move pc debug settings by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2459\n* decomp `bigmap` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2460\n* ci: check for incorrect assert usage in C++ files by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2461\n* d/jak2: cleaning up some old decomp issues by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2462\n* docs/issues: attempt to clarify what version is for the game/OpenGOAL by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2467\n* Update README.md by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2468\n* repl: add `gameVersionFolder` to repl-config for running the non-default version by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2463\n* cli: ensure an overridden project path is absolute by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2464\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2466\n* gk: fix "reboot in debug" option not working properly when `gk` has no args by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2469\n* [jak2] fix disappearing guard by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2470\n* [jak2] more nav-related nan fixes by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2472\n* [jak2] fix hitting enemies after they die by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2475\n* fix jak 2 text encoding/decoding + minor decomp type fixes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2476\n* add a toggle for faster airlocks and elevators and enable by default by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2478\n* jak 2 memcard support by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2482\n* [jak2] misc fixes to renderers by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2488\n* fix viewport not being set for probe draw by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2489\n* [jak 2] Add generic and warp by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2495\n* [jak2] fix generic crashes by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2505\n* update collision renderer for jak 2 by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2508\n* [jak2] Disable envmap hack if warp effect is enabled by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2511\n* g/j2: temporarily disable some `gui-control` code to fix rock avalanche by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2510\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2514\n* more generic fixes by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2515\n* d/jak2: fix `dig-sinking-plat`s in dig3 by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2519\n* d/jak2: decompile missing function in `whack` by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2521\n* d/jak2: temp fix for rewarding orbs from talker speeches by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2523\n* game: Remove temporary CLI arg shim in `gk` by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2532\n* [jak2] bring other version fixes to source by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2528\n* fix some decomp types and get rid of in-game frame time perception by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2535\n* Do not swap between clocks for airlocks speed by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2537\n* Fix bad `lsack` level borrow by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2540\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2542\n* scripts: support new jak 2 decompiler config versions via `task` by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2543\n* formatter: add tree-sitter dependency and commit early draft work on a proper code formatter by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2536\n* jak2: fix 3d hud elements not drawing by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2527\n* Create a new format for particle definitions (`defpart`) by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2572\n* subtitles-editor: Allow removing lines and fix some issues by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2573\n* jak2: fix warp effect for robotank and underb on other aspect ratios by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2574\n* fix many instances of bad bone data being used by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2580\n* less branches for division + fix divide by zeros by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2585\n* jak2: overlord rework by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2544\n* attempting to slightly optimize `defpart` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2587\n* [jak2] more specific cutscene detection by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2590\n* allow quoting `:key` symbols + further optimize `defpart` by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2592\n* fix minimap stretch by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2593\n* [jak2] Fix temp stacks being created outside process stack by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2595\n* g/j2: remove temporary hack to allow the avalanche to play by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2599\n* [jak2] try to speed up compile a bit by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2596\n* settings: handle corrupted json settings files by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2600\n* ci: speed up unit-test execution by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2586\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.34...v0.1.35',
