    body: "## What's Changed\n* [merc2] support vertex updates, use this for blerc in jak 1 and jak 2 by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2179\n* d/jak2: cleaning up the remainder of unblocked / unclaimed files by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2171\n* More DGOs in Jak2 inputs.jsonc by @BreakPoints in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2182\n* [jak2] pc-hook for pris texture upload by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2184\n* Minor fix for Rock Village IL speedrun by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2187\n* Create Hungarian translation of game text for Jak 1 by @LuminarLight in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2141\n* Jak2 decomp/hover formation by @chillypepper in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2028\n* d/jak2: finish `onin-game` and resolve type-hinting `(array object)` elements by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2188\n* [decomp] finish up `nav-graph`, `traffic-engine`, `traffic-manager`, `height-map` by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2191\n* Autosplitter - add per-level fly & orb counts by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2192\n* decomp: `citizen-*` files, `metalhead-*` files, `civilian`, `guard`, `hal3-course` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2194\n* ci: allow manually updating the controller db by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2200\n* decomp: `hover-*` files, `wasp`, `crimson-guard-hover`, `flamer`, `target-turret`, `drill-turret`, `jellyfish` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2198\n* d/jak2: `seal-at-waterslums` working, and do a pass through all missions by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2199\n* ci: switch to a pull request instead of a direct commit for updating controller db by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2201\n* [jak 2] add lightning renderer by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2203\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2202\n* [jak2] fix alpha test in lightning by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2204\n* [jak2] improve loader for jak 2 levels by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2206\n* jak2: fix `drill-eggs` crash by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2209\n* decomp: `castle-baron` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2208\n* decomp: `metalkor-*` files by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2211\n* [tie] support per-proto visibility flags by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2212\n* split new pc features in some files into their own code files + address some old issues + ripple graphics improvements by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2216\n* [jak1] force credits to use audio language instead of text language by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2220\n* Easier combo for Speedrun Options by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2196\n* decomp: `meet-brutter` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2218\n* decomp: `kidesc-*|crocesc-*` files, `ash4-course` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2219\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2217\n* decomp: `race-*` files by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2224\n* set up fog for jak 2 by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2223\n* decomp: `palcab-obs` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2222\n* [jak1] fix crash on startup by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2225\n* Redundant `(declare-file (debug))` by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2226\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2231\n* docs: Automatically generate documentation from goal_src code by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2214\n* Speedrun verification text cleanup by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2229\n* [jak2] add sprite glow renderer by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2232\n* ci: set cmake preset in informing workflow by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2237\n* ci: gen-docs propagate the runId since thats the best we can do by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2238\n* [jak2] fix rare civilian flee crash by @VodBox in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2230\n* jak2: add back some pc port debugging tools and add `palace-scenes` to gsrc by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2240\n* Fix Jak 2 warp gates by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2244\n* repl: prevent REPL crash when running `(reload)` by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2243\n* [goalc] reduce compiler memory usage by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2247\n* port `pckernel` to Jak 2 by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2248\n* [decomp] `ctywide-obs` by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2250\n* [jak2] text aspect ratio fixes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2251\n* [jak 2] fix boot, increase level heap sizes by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2252\n* [jak2] fix foreground light calculation by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2254\n* Fix Jak 2 scissoring by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2257\n* [sprite glow] fix crashes by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2256\n* [jak2] fix highly aggressive guard zoomer ambush by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2264\n* [windows] make the games start up in the user's preferred system UI language by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2267\n* d/jak2: finish `forest-obs` by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2266\n* [jak2] fix palace rotation and sprite glow depth test by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2269\n* Add Speedrun Category Extensions by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2195\n* [jak2] fix crash with `*print-column*` loading the wrong memory by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2281\n* jak2: fix `jellyfish` crash and temporarily disable underwater warp by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2270\n* rotate log files by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2283\n* CI: Periodic Controller Database Update by @OpenGOALBot in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2287\n* [jak2] merc lod hacks + region debugger + make level heap less massive by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2285\n* decomp: `ruf-*`, `jinx-*`, `mog-*`, `grim-*`, `hosehead-*` files, `gun-buoy` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2279\n* dbgr: allow dumping the backtrace to a file by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2284\n* docs: fix method docstrings and grab `@file` comment blocks to use as a file description by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2289\n* [jak2] minor decomp cleanup + add force actors and sprite pc hacks by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2291\n\n## New Contributors\n* @OpenGOALBot made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2217\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.32...v0.1.33",
