    body: "## What's Changed\n* decomp: `target-tube` by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2041\n* [jak 2] merc by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2039\n* d/jak2: decomp a bunch of files related to the beginning of the game by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2043\n* lights, death, and rotation fix by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2042\n* 989snd: Support version >= 2 sound effects by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1991\n* format, fix decompiler crash by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2044\n* Assorted sound fixes by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2049\n* d/jak2: add missing ref tests for files that can be added to ref tests by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2061\n* offline-test: Partition by DGO and colorize/condense output by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2045\n* d/jak2: pass through all simple / non-blocked `*-part`, `*-ocean` and `*-scenes` files by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2048\n* Fix EarTrans assignment by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2057\n* jak2: misc fixes by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2050\n* support c++ tools on macos by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2063\n* CI: Add a macOS Github runner by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2064\n* jak1: fix debug menu regression around `lambda`s by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2065\n* decomp: output mips2c method/function declarations to the `_disasm.gc` file by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2054\n* d/jak2: finish remaining `*-h` files that aren't in progress or spoken for by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2059\n* [jak2] split up big dgos, some minor cleanup by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2066\n* decomp: add explicit failures for common config mistakes related to allowed_objs by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2062\n* [decomp] fix up `gun` decomp by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2067\n* add target-board-handler by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2068\n* d/jak2: finish `atoll-scenes` by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2069\n* [decomp] drawable, memory-usage by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2070\n* Prevent putting nullptr into child sound list by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2072\n* decomp: don't mutate allowed/banned object lists by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/2073\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.30...v0.1.31",
