    body: "## What's Changed\n* Added first working instance of controller/keyboard re-mapper by @animalstyletaco in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1702\n* scripts: Add a (hopefully) better goal_src updating script by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1769\n* tests: allow the binary prep steps in the linux release script to be skipped by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1772\n* HUD - show total/level counts on dpad up/down by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1756\n* add a bunch of new cheat codes & re-do all pc cheat codes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1770\n* Fixed invalid cursor mode bug in GLDisplay::update_cursor_visibility() by @animalstyletaco in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1774\n* Improvements for stuttering by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1768\n* game: add a speedrunner mode which enables a faster new-game/resetting experience by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1773\n* game: windowed mode related fixes by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1778\n* [game] cutscene skipping by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1779\n* game: add new cheats to debug menu by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1780\n* add option to disable mouse hiding by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1782\n\n## New Contributors\n* @animalstyletaco made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1702\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.24...v0.1.25",
