    body: "## What's Changed\r\n* tests: Cleanup decompiler test fixtures and try to improve the test output / add a readable report by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1724\r\n* game/imgui: remove V-Sync checkbox as it can't be interacted with by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1726\r\n* Add a gltf level exporter by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1719\r\n* [custom levels] add invisible option by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1729\r\n* [custom levels] add collide mode option by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1730\r\n* gsrc: add decomp begins placeholder to all gsrc files by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1731\r\n* all-types: Improve Jak 2's all-types by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1728\r\n* fix crash when importing glb by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1732\r\n* decomp/lsp: Differentiate warnings from likely/definite errors by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1725\r\n* cleanup cheats menu + change game territory logic + some subtitles by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1733\r\n* goal_src: Get rid of `*OLD*` files in jak1's goal_src by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1736\r\n* [decompiler] handle types without inspects better in all-types by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1735\r\n* Update intro video in the README.md by @mpope9 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1744\r\n* Clean up useless logging in 989snd by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1748\r\n* fix invincibility cheat codes + some japan-specific changes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1750\r\n* Implement IOP semaphores. by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1747\r\n* fix bug in knuth RNG by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1757\r\n* Run IOP Vblank handler on the IOP thread by @Ziemas in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1752\r\n* Support 4 controllers by @dallmeyer in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1751\r\n* custom levels: add support for more res types in actor lumps by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1754\r\n* ref: update pad_REF by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1761\r\n* fix a game bug and add a new compiler feature by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1758\r\n* Update Readme to include missing dependencies on Fedora and Arch installations by @liamh101 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1763\r\n* Add dockerfiles for Linux environments with documentation by @liamh101 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1764\r\n* ci: add back the windows artifact by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1766\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @mpope9 made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1744\r\n* @liamh101 made their first contribution in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1763\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.22...v0.1.24",
