    body: "## What's Changed\n* change default window settings by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1656\n* fix misc options being swapped by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1658\n* [gfx] fix merc/generic eye detection by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1657\n* CI: Cleanup release process by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1659\n* [high fps] fix target-racer by @Brent-Hickey in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1661\n* allow select pause in retail mode by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1665\n* Cleanup goalc tests, fix jak2 kernel bugs by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1669\n* Pc port debug small qol by @Zedb0T in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1663\n* [graphics] some blit optimizations by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1667\n* change out folder for Windows release w/ debug info by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1671\n* make aux list not get cleared when game is paused by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1673\n* [graphics] fix flutflut eye drawing with merc by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1674\n* game: add secrets menu, music player and some more pc settings to the debug menu by @Hat-Kid in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1664\n* LSP: initial LSP implementation for IR files to assist with decompilation by @xTVaser in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1647\n* implement a cheats menu + a few bug fixes by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1677\n* [graphics] switch to depth-pass shadows by @water111 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1681\n* Depth Cue by @Francessco121 in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1676\n* fix borderless on Windows, resolution when letterboxes and envmap setting by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1683\n* fix controller vibration by @ManDude in https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/pull/1685\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/open-goal/jak-project/compare/v0.1.19...v0.1.20",
